4
00:01:46,420 --> 00:01:47,420
- Bagus!
- Serang!

5
00:01:47,420 --> 00:01:48,260
Bagus!

6
00:01:48,990 --> 00:01:49,830
Halang dia!

7
00:01:55,550 --> 00:01:56,390
Hantaran yang bagus.

8
00:02:00,910 --> 00:02:01,750
Hebatnya!

9
00:02:02,990 --> 00:02:03,830
Itu pun boleh disambut?

10
00:02:04,140 --> 00:02:05,550
Pergi!

11
00:02:06,910 --> 00:02:08,230
- Pergi!
- Serang!

12
00:02:08,230 --> 00:02:09,390
Lajunya!

13
00:02:12,550 --> 00:02:13,670
Masuk!

14
00:02:13,670 --> 00:02:14,990
Cantik!

15
00:02:15,180 --> 00:02:17,350
- Bagus!
- Bagus!

16
00:02:17,580 --> 00:02:19,140
- Bagus!
- Bagus!

17
00:02:28,550 --> 00:02:30,620
- Bagus!
- Bagus!

18
00:02:37,180 --> 00:02:38,020
Bagus!

19
00:02:44,350 --> 00:02:45,390
Baguslah.

20
00:02:56,140 --> 00:02:56,980
Masuk!

21
00:02:57,230 --> 00:02:58,740
Cantik!

22
00:02:59,070 --> 00:02:59,910
- Bagus!
- Bagus!

23
00:03:04,510 --> 00:03:05,700
Kerjasama yang baik.

24
00:03:05,990 --> 00:03:06,830
Teruskan.

25
00:03:08,230 --> 00:03:09,070
Meng Wan,

26
00:03:10,140 --> 00:03:10,980
saya sukakan awak.

27
00:03:12,110 --> 00:03:13,580
Saya tahu, saya pun suka awak juga.

28
00:03:13,740 --> 00:03:14,580
Mari, cepat main bola.

29
00:03:14,580 --> 00:03:15,420
Meng Wan,

30
00:03:16,110 --> 00:03:16,950
saya serius.

31
00:03:17,300 --> 00:03:18,790
Semasa di Liangzhou lagi,
saya dah nak beritahu awak.

32
00:03:21,880 --> 00:03:24,810
♪Harapan, atau♪

33
00:03:26,950 --> 00:03:28,020
Perlawanan belum tamat lagi.

34
00:03:30,990 --> 00:03:31,900
Kalau macam itu,
tunggu perlawanan tamat.

35
00:03:32,790 --> 00:03:33,630
Saya tunggu awak.

36
00:03:36,820 --> 00:03:40,420
♪Sesali diri mengapa teragak-agak♪

37
00:03:40,840 --> 00:03:44,380
♪Tidak berani mendekat lagi♪

38
00:03:44,670 --> 00:03:47,330
♪Sembunyikan segalanya♪

39
00:03:47,610 --> 00:03:52,050
♪Segala yang ingin diungkapkan
terhenti seketika♪

40
00:03:52,360 --> 00:03:55,840
♪Betapa ingin memeluk
susuk tubuh itu dengan erat♪

41
00:03:56,270 --> 00:03:59,920
♪Melangkah berasingan
setelah terjaga dari mimpi♪

42
00:04:00,150 --> 00:04:08,270
♪Memerhatikan segala masa lalu
yang belum berakhir♪

43
00:04:19,710 --> 00:04:20,860
- Kuda itu terkejut!
- Kuda itu terkejut!

44
00:04:20,990 --> 00:04:21,910
Kuda itu terkejut!

45
00:04:22,380 --> 00:04:23,940
Hati-hati!

46
00:04:24,150 --> 00:04:25,030
Cepat ke tepi!

47
00:04:25,380 --> 00:04:26,260
Elak!

48
00:04:59,740 --> 00:05:00,710
Bahayanya!

49
00:05:00,860 --> 00:05:01,700
Yalah.

50
00:05:21,860 --> 00:05:25,720
♪Sesali diri mengapa teragak-agak♪

51
00:05:27,030 --> 00:05:28,180
Adakah tulang belakang awak lebih keras

52
00:05:28,180 --> 00:05:29,030
daripada telapuk kuda liar itu?

53
00:05:29,790 --> 00:05:30,630
Awak cuma seorang sasterawan.

54
00:05:30,940 --> 00:05:31,780
Jangan paksa diri.

55
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:36,540
♪Segala yang ingin diungkapkan
terhenti seketika♪

56
00:05:36,620 --> 00:05:37,460
Awak tak apa-apa?

57
00:05:39,420 --> 00:05:40,260
Tak ada apa-apa.

58
00:05:41,350 --> 00:05:44,990
♪Melangkah berasingan
setelah terjaga dari mimpi♪

59
00:05:45,260 --> 00:05:46,740
Terima kasih kerana
menyelamatkan saya, Pegawai Fang.

60
00:05:47,010 --> 00:05:53,610
♪Segala masa lalu yang belum berakhir♪

61
00:06:07,150 --> 00:06:07,990
Saya tak apa-apa.

62
00:06:08,940 --> 00:06:09,820
Saya pergi ambilkan ubat untuk awak.

63
00:06:11,380 --> 00:06:12,350
Terima kasih, Cik He.

64
00:06:12,410 --> 00:06:15,770
♪Biarkan kenangan berterbangan♪

65
00:06:16,180 --> 00:06:18,880
♪Mengutip sendirian♪

66
00:06:19,080 --> 00:06:23,440
♪Kelopak bunga yang berwarna-warni
bagaikan hari musim bunga yang hangat♪

67
00:06:23,850 --> 00:06:27,530
♪Menunggu masa lalu menjadi tenang♪

68
00:06:27,770 --> 00:06:31,310
♪Berubah menjadi
cahaya langit yang bersih♪

69
00:06:31,540 --> 00:06:39,620
♪Angin bertiup lagi,
membawa impianku dengan lembut♪

70
00:06:41,670 --> 00:06:42,510
Cik Duan.

71
00:06:44,230 --> 00:06:45,120
Cik Duan,

72
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:46,160
awak terkejut tadi.

73
00:06:47,260 --> 00:06:48,710
Ini Pil Qingxin untuk menenangkan jiwa,

74
00:06:49,550 --> 00:06:50,670
boleh bantu awak tenangkan fikiran.

75
00:06:53,990 --> 00:06:54,860
Terima kasih, Tuan Muda Wang.

76
00:06:55,940 --> 00:06:57,030
Cik Duan, sama-sama.

77
00:07:02,420 --> 00:07:04,110
Memandangkan keluarga kita
sudah bertunang,

78
00:07:04,910 --> 00:07:06,470
maka kita akan menjadi sekeluarga nanti.

79
00:07:06,790 --> 00:07:08,060
Kita patut lebih kerap melawat,

80
00:07:08,060 --> 00:07:08,910
dan saling mengenali
dengan lebih mendalam.

81
00:07:08,910 --> 00:07:09,750
Mungkin selepas ini,

82
00:07:09,760 --> 00:07:10,860
hubungan kita
akan jadi lebih rapat, kan?

83
00:07:11,910 --> 00:07:12,770
Tuan Muda Wang,

84
00:07:12,780 --> 00:07:13,790
sila jaga batas awak.

85
00:07:14,380 --> 00:07:15,220
Cik Duan,

86
00:07:15,590 --> 00:07:17,030
tadi masa awak elak kuda liar itu,

87
00:07:17,030 --> 00:07:18,030
awak tak sengaja tercicir barang.

88
00:07:18,420 --> 00:07:19,350
Jika awak tak kisah,

89
00:07:19,710 --> 00:07:20,590
biar saya hantarkannya kepada awak.

90
00:07:23,550 --> 00:07:24,790
Segan pula nak
menyusahkan awak, Pegawai Fang.

91
00:07:25,060 --> 00:07:26,180
Biar saya sendiri
yang pergi mengambilnya.

92
00:07:26,860 --> 00:07:27,700
Silakan, cik.

93
00:07:38,590 --> 00:07:39,710
Tak sangka terdapat ramai jelitawan

94
00:07:39,710 --> 00:07:40,820
di kediaman Duan ini.

95
00:07:41,940 --> 00:07:43,300
Siapakah jelitawan ini?

96
00:07:43,300 --> 00:07:44,570
- Berambus.
- Awak!

97
00:07:57,420 --> 00:07:58,260
Pegawai Fang,

98
00:07:59,180 --> 00:08:00,790
apa barang yang saya tercicir tadi?

99
00:08:03,350 --> 00:08:04,940
Tadi itu cuma helah saya sahaja.

100
00:08:06,230 --> 00:08:07,670
Saya tak nampak
awak tercicir apa-apa pun.

101
00:08:08,550 --> 00:08:10,190
Saya cuma nampak awak
dalam kesulitan di sana,

102
00:08:10,670 --> 00:08:11,510
lalu saya terfikir

103
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:12,640
mungkin awak perlukan

104
00:08:12,640 --> 00:08:13,620
alasan untuk beredar.

105
00:08:17,500 --> 00:08:19,470
Dari mana awak nampak
yang saya sedang gelisah?

106
00:08:20,420 --> 00:08:21,500
Bukankah awak macam nak menangis?

107
00:08:23,710 --> 00:08:24,550
Menangis?

108
00:08:25,030 --> 00:08:25,870
Di sini.

109
00:08:27,550 --> 00:08:28,390
Dekat sini?

110
00:08:36,830 --> 00:08:37,950
Lihat betul-betul.

111
00:08:38,470 --> 00:08:40,020
Ini ialah solekan air mata.

112
00:08:40,380 --> 00:08:42,190
Inilah gaya solekan
yang paling popular sekarang.

113
00:08:42,350 --> 00:08:43,500
Saya bukannya nak menangis pun.

114
00:08:43,950 --> 00:08:44,790
Tengoklah.

115
00:09:02,110 --> 00:09:03,020
Dah elok-elok,

116
00:09:03,620 --> 00:09:05,110
kenapa nak lukis muka
nampak macam nak menangis?

117
00:09:05,990 --> 00:09:06,830
Ketawa

118
00:09:07,070 --> 00:09:08,430
jauh lebih baik daripada menangis,

119
00:09:08,950 --> 00:09:09,790
bukan begitu?

120
00:09:12,430 --> 00:09:13,620
Apa yang awak tahu?

121
00:09:14,190 --> 00:09:15,030
Solekan jenis ini

122
00:09:15,380 --> 00:09:16,540
baru akan nampak

123
00:09:16,540 --> 00:09:18,140
lemah lembut dan
mengundang belas kasihan.

124
00:09:19,190 --> 00:09:20,310
Saya memang tak faham.

125
00:09:21,590 --> 00:09:22,660
Selama ini saya sangka

126
00:09:22,860 --> 00:09:23,990
wanita yang menyerlah

127
00:09:23,990 --> 00:09:25,310
seperti awak,

128
00:09:25,590 --> 00:09:26,830
tidak perlu rasa kasihan.

129
00:10:10,070 --> 00:10:10,910
Pegawai Fang,

130
00:10:11,860 --> 00:10:13,380
sebenarnya lebih baik
awak jadi diri sendiri.

131
00:10:14,660 --> 00:10:16,110
Awak tak perlu ikut cara Abang Xu.

132
00:10:30,540 --> 00:10:31,470
Cik He.

133
00:10:41,860 --> 00:10:42,740
Dia sukakan awak.

134
00:10:44,900 --> 00:10:46,960
Cik He, janganlah
cakap bukan-bukan. Saya...

135
00:10:46,970 --> 00:10:48,380
Tadi masa kuda itu terkejut,

136
00:10:48,590 --> 00:10:49,710
semua orang melarikan diri,

137
00:10:50,140 --> 00:10:51,380
hanya dia yang terus meluru ke sini

138
00:10:51,380 --> 00:10:52,260
untuk melindungi awak.

139
00:10:52,260 --> 00:10:53,860
Dia hampir cedera parah sebab itu.

140
00:10:54,950 --> 00:10:55,830
Pada pandangan saya,

141
00:10:55,830 --> 00:10:56,780
berdasarkan keadaan dia,

142
00:10:57,540 --> 00:10:58,380
walaupun terpaksa gadaikan nyawa

143
00:10:58,590 --> 00:10:59,430
demi awak,

144
00:10:59,590 --> 00:11:00,470
dia juga sanggup.

145
00:11:01,500 --> 00:11:02,350
Bagus! Hantaran yang bagus!

146
00:11:02,780 --> 00:11:04,540
- Bagus!
- Bagusnya!

147
00:11:05,260 --> 00:11:07,900
- Bagus!
- Bagus!

148
00:11:08,070 --> 00:11:08,910
Hebatnya!

149
00:11:11,230 --> 00:11:12,430
Gol yang cantik!

150
00:11:13,500 --> 00:11:15,260
Abang Xu, cantik!

151
00:11:32,020 --> 00:11:34,140
(Walaupun dia orang jianghu,)

152
00:11:34,710 --> 00:11:36,740
(jadi kakak ipar ketiga saya
pun bagus juga.)

153
00:12:09,620 --> 00:12:10,900
Apa awak buat ini?

154
00:12:12,830 --> 00:12:13,710
Tadi saya serius.

155
00:12:15,260 --> 00:12:16,100
Saya sukakan awak.

156
00:12:22,470 --> 00:12:23,590
Semenjak pulang ke Nandu,

157
00:12:24,260 --> 00:12:25,710
setiap kali dengar awak
temu jodoh dengan orang lain,

158
00:12:25,710 --> 00:12:26,830
saya rasa sangat risau dan marah.

159
00:12:28,020 --> 00:12:29,310
Risau sebab takut
awak terima orang lain,

160
00:12:29,950 --> 00:12:31,110
marah sebab marahkan diri sendiri,

161
00:12:32,260 --> 00:12:33,380
dah lama saya sukakan awak,

162
00:12:34,070 --> 00:12:35,110
tapi tak berani nak beritahu awak.

163
00:12:36,590 --> 00:12:37,430
Meng Wan,

164
00:12:38,350 --> 00:12:39,540
hari ini saya dah nekad.

165
00:12:40,900 --> 00:12:41,900
Saya mesti beritahu awak.

166
00:12:43,740 --> 00:12:44,580
Ini...

167
00:12:44,860 --> 00:12:45,700
Meng Wan.

168
00:12:48,140 --> 00:12:49,260
Habis itu, apa yang
awak suka tentang saya?

169
00:12:51,020 --> 00:12:51,860
Saya pun tak tahu.

170
00:12:53,230 --> 00:12:54,190
Namun, saya memang sukakan awak.

171
00:12:55,190 --> 00:12:56,110
Apa yang awak suka tentang saya pun

172
00:12:56,110 --> 00:12:57,070
awak tak boleh nak jelaskan,

173
00:12:57,070 --> 00:12:58,020
kenapa saya perlu percayakan awak?

174
00:12:58,170 --> 00:12:59,020
Andai saya boleh jelaskan,

175
00:12:59,020 --> 00:12:59,860
awak sudi terima saya?

176
00:13:00,110 --> 00:13:00,950
Siapa yang cakap?

177
00:13:03,260 --> 00:13:04,100
Meng Wan.

178
00:13:07,310 --> 00:13:08,430
Saya benar-benar sukakan awak.

179
00:13:10,540 --> 00:13:12,310
Saya suka awak yang lurus dan tegak,

180
00:13:13,740 --> 00:13:14,830
ada pendapat sendiri.

181
00:13:16,590 --> 00:13:18,070
Saya suka awak yang tidak berpura-pura,

182
00:13:18,830 --> 00:13:19,860
buat kerja dengan tangkas.

183
00:13:22,830 --> 00:13:23,670
Saya juga sukakan awak

184
00:13:24,020 --> 00:13:24,900
kerana tidak gentar langsung

185
00:13:25,990 --> 00:13:26,950
apabila berhadapan dengan musuh.

186
00:13:28,380 --> 00:13:29,220
Sudah tentu,

187
00:13:30,260 --> 00:13:31,430
saya juga suka awak yang menarik.

188
00:13:34,830 --> 00:13:35,670
Dahlah,

189
00:13:36,140 --> 00:13:36,980
saya dah tahu.

190
00:13:38,740 --> 00:13:39,780
"Dahlah,

191
00:13:40,470 --> 00:13:41,590
saya dah tahu" itu apa maksudnya?

192
00:13:42,190 --> 00:13:43,310
"Dah tahu" maksudnya dah tahulah.

193
00:13:43,900 --> 00:13:44,740
Jadi...

194
00:13:45,110 --> 00:13:46,140
Jadi awak terimalah ini?

195
00:13:46,140 --> 00:13:46,990
Saya tak cakap pun.

196
00:13:48,430 --> 00:13:49,950
Habis itu apa maksudnya?
Awak kena jelaskan.

197
00:13:49,950 --> 00:13:51,110
Kenapa banyak sangat soalan awak ini?

198
00:13:51,540 --> 00:13:52,590
Dahlah, saya dah tahu.

199
00:14:04,950 --> 00:14:06,230
Awak suka penampilan saya hari ini?

200
00:14:07,780 --> 00:14:08,620
Boleh tahan.

201
00:14:09,110 --> 00:14:10,540
Segala-galanya membara,
bendera berkibar,

202
00:14:10,860 --> 00:14:12,260
seorang pemuda gagah yang memacu kuda.

203
00:14:15,500 --> 00:14:16,350
Asalkan awak suka, itu sudah memadai.

204
00:14:18,380 --> 00:14:19,310
Saya mahu awak melihat

205
00:14:19,540 --> 00:14:20,500
semangat kehidupan di dunia ini,

206
00:14:21,230 --> 00:14:22,140
dan juga mahu awak melihat

207
00:14:24,070 --> 00:14:25,020
diri saya yang
paling jujur dan menyerlah.

208
00:14:25,860 --> 00:14:27,230
Niat kecil awak itu,

209
00:14:27,590 --> 00:14:28,830
saya sudah tentu tahu.

210
00:14:56,740 --> 00:14:58,260
Sepuluh hari akan
berakhir tidak lama lagi.

211
00:14:59,660 --> 00:15:00,950
Masa berlalu dengan pantas, ya.

212
00:15:02,500 --> 00:15:03,340
Simu,

213
00:15:05,350 --> 00:15:06,710
apa perasaan awak
tentang dunia kali ini?

214
00:15:13,540 --> 00:15:14,740
Dunia ini

215
00:15:20,500 --> 00:15:22,230
memang sebuah karya seni yang indah.

216
00:15:47,170 --> 00:15:48,020
Lagu yang bagus.

217
00:15:48,020 --> 00:15:48,860
Ya.

218
00:15:49,590 --> 00:15:50,430
Hebat.

219
00:16:01,590 --> 00:16:02,830
- Hebat.
- Lagu yang bagus.

220
00:16:02,830 --> 00:16:03,710
Sangat hebat.

221
00:16:03,710 --> 00:16:04,740
Kemahiran bermain guqin Cik Luo Xian

222
00:16:04,740 --> 00:16:05,620
memang sangat luar biasa.

223
00:16:05,830 --> 00:16:07,070
- Betul itu.
- Hebat.

224
00:16:07,260 --> 00:16:08,100
Ya.

225
00:16:09,140 --> 00:16:09,980
Mari.

226
00:16:10,540 --> 00:16:11,990
Puan, awak kelihatan

227
00:16:11,990 --> 00:16:12,990
sangat bersemangat hari ini,

228
00:16:13,190 --> 00:16:14,140
perasaan tenang.

229
00:16:14,140 --> 00:16:14,980
Yakah?

230
00:16:16,110 --> 00:16:17,070
Awak salah tengok rasanya.

231
00:16:18,710 --> 00:16:19,740
Sudah Pukul Hai pun.

232
00:16:20,310 --> 00:16:21,620
Waktu bekerja awak sudah lama tamat.

233
00:16:21,620 --> 00:16:22,460
Minum secawan lagi.

234
00:16:22,590 --> 00:16:23,710
Baliklah berehat awal.

235
00:16:24,470 --> 00:16:25,310
- Namun...
- Mari minum secawan lagi.

236
00:16:25,620 --> 00:16:26,660
Awak masih ada tetamu.

237
00:16:27,170 --> 00:16:28,010
- Sila.
- Sila.

238
00:16:28,860 --> 00:16:29,860
Hari ini pengecualian.

239
00:16:31,470 --> 00:16:32,830
Saya dan semua orang di Rumah Yuzao

240
00:16:33,660 --> 00:16:34,950
akan berseronok sepuas hati.

241
00:16:34,950 --> 00:16:35,910
Ada apa-apa berita aneh

242
00:16:35,910 --> 00:16:36,950
di Nandu baru-baru ini?

243
00:16:37,470 --> 00:16:38,740
Berita yang paling besar itu

244
00:16:39,140 --> 00:16:40,610
hal Wang Jin, bukan?

245
00:16:40,830 --> 00:16:41,740
Dengar kata,

246
00:16:41,740 --> 00:16:42,780
Timbalan Menteri
Pejabat Kehakiman Diraja,

247
00:16:42,890 --> 00:16:43,760
Wang Jin,

248
00:16:43,760 --> 00:16:44,950
rupanya seorang putera.

249
00:16:46,740 --> 00:16:47,860
Sudah terlambat.

250
00:16:48,110 --> 00:16:49,430
Sekarang dia sudah
